{
  "stem": "4753.9",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had no toothbrush or things like that, so that was no question.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Naturally, when we had the smallest chance to get a drop of water, we washed our hands, or our face, or taking a bath when we could.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as a daily basis, you couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they took us back to Auschwitz where we arrived to the crematorium, for some reason, they took us a few times back for showers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we washed ourselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then sprayed us with some yellow stuff-- so-called disinfection lotion, what was very horrible, because they were pinching our skin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But sometime-- I don't know how, maybe it rained-- one time, I collected water in a dish, and I started to wash myself.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how, an SS man-- and that was inside the barracks, but no glass panel-- an SS man saw me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't saw him, and came in, took the water, poured it out, and beat me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't ever take it tragically.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somehow you get used to the idea that you have no rights, or you cannot do anything about anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you was beaten, that was the normal things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not the normal feeling, because you felt the pain, but--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They inflicted us with typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had typhus too, and malaria, and diphtheria, different kind of sicknesses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And naturally, later-- many months later-- I heard there were [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] other people infected by them, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They wanted us to die.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was no problem if you had diphtheria or malaria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never got in hospital in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were not any activity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You prayed, yourself, quietly, but not openly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no need to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
